== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
《中央情爆員》獲得了兩極的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度71%，基於188條評論，平均分為5.8/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/central_intelligence/ |title=Central Intelligence (2016) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-06-16 |archive-date=2019-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728144220/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/central_intelligence/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分52<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/central-intelligence |title=Central Intelligence reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-06-16 |archive-date=2019-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619111140/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/central-intelligence |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.5分。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，電影於2016年6月17日與《[[海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒？|海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒？]]》共同上映；在其首映週末，預計能從3508間戲院中獲得約3000萬左右的票房<ref name=budget/>。美國首映週末票房為3450萬美元位居亞軍，排於冠軍《[[海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒？|海底總動員2：多莉去哪兒？]]》（1.36億美元）之後<ref name="Friday">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/finding-dory-box-office-central-intelligence-captain-america-totals-1201774498/ |title='Dory's Record Animated Pic $136M+ Opening Is Also Second Best For June After ‘Jurassic World’ |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-06-20 |archive-date=2016-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620191652/http://deadline.com/2016/06/finding-dory-box-office-central-intelligence-captain-america-totals-1201774498/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

